Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.71,0:00:13.52,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidentally, the second I got the \Nnerve to turn around, Azuki turned too.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.98,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,The seconds felt like hours.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.48,0:00:20.08,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Then I came to my senses \Nand turned away quickly.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.28,0:00:25.74,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,But two or three seconds later, I \Ncouldn't help turning around again.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.90,0:00:33.23,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Farther away, Azuki turned again too.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.47,0:00:43.03,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Azuki and I were \Non the exact same wavelength.
