Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.60,0:02:12.77,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wavelength?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.95,0:02:17.45,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,She could've turned ten times, and \Nyour eyes just only met twice.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.04,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.87,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Your conviction is \Nimpressive. I don't get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.60,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,You making fun of me?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.27,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Course not. I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.29,0:02:30.27,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,In sixth grade, I laid eyes \Non Azuki for the first time.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.25,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,We went to Akehi Elementary \Nbut she went to Akehi Second.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.93,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,At the school swimming competition,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.93,0:02:41.66,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki and I kept staring at each \Nother from opposing sidelines.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.94,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't embarrassed at all, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HBA9ABC&\fnBalzano\b1\pos(334,112)}Entrance \N Ceremony
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.63,0:02:53.36,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes met again at the middle \Nschool entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.11,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,This time we were only a few feet apart,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.63,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,but we turned away quickly.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.45,0:03:08.45,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,This has been going on since elementary \Nschool? You might as well have been dating.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.25,0:03:12.53,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's only with very optimistic hindsight.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.53,0:03:14.42,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter how perfectly \Nin tune you guys are,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.00,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't get her e-mail, \Nyou can't communicate.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.42,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, as long as I \Nget it before we graduate.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.32,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we focus on manga!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.15,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.40,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's five pages for you then.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.18,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.84,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I was working on it while you \Ntook your trip down memory lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HA6A2A5&\fnBurst My Bubble\frz5.849\frx8\fry356\pos(588,201)}Two Planet Earths
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.35,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,"Two Earths."
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.97,0:03:38.81,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,The planet we live on is just \Na clone of the real Earth.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.81,0:03:43.61,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,We too, are merely clones of \Nthat planet's inhabitants.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.61,0:03:48.07,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,We were created as mere \Ncomponents of their experiment.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.80,0:03:56.36,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,They recreated their own condition in order \Nto observe and learn how to make a better world.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.96,0:04:03.70,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of this experiment, there's no \Nwar or global warming on the {\i1}real{\i0} Earth.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.26,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Shujin.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.17,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.58,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.15,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Names can't be done on a whim!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.15,0:04:16.25,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how to make a \Ngood layout. And my pictures—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.48,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Is this story copied from somewhere?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.81,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not copied, but there might be some \Noverlapping elements. That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.19,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a story anyone could come up with.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.34,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Not just {\i1}anyone{\i0} could come up with this.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.30,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,At least, I for sure couldn't!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.23,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.81,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,This setting has me totally spellbound.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.40,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.30,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.30,0:04:37.81,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,But after that, it just becomes a battle \Nbetween us and the people from the real Earth.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.74,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's what captivated me!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.19,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,You can jump straight into a battle!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.49,0:04:45.08,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you have an even better idea?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.10,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about doing a sports manga too.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.36,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe call it "The Sunglasses Pitcher"?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.06,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.67,0:04:58.76,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,A Little League fastball pitcher who's aiming \Nto be pro, gets hit by a line drive and goes blind.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.08,0:05:04.82,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years later, a pitcher with sunglasses \Nsuddenly appears in the pro league.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.82,0:05:11.30,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,He has a perfect game, able to throw \Nany pitch, any course, at 180km.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.12,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,The startling truth is that the young \Nboy didn't give up on his dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.75,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,He trained extensively with \Nhis father for ten years.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.68,Alt,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Get on your feet, sunglasses!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.71,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dad!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.71,0:05:28.84,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,When it gets out that he's blind, the boy must \Nface the league administrators and other pitchers.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.26,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, Shujin!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.03,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't think up such an \Nelaborate story in such a setting!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.05,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.90,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You really think I'm good?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.58,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Normally I think you're stupid—
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.15,Alt,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.91,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually been thinking about \Nit frantically every day...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.91,0:05:45.06,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You know how sometimes, I'm \Nkind of overly confident?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.79,0:05:49.41,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe in me, I have \Na real reason to be confident.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.21,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.34,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously so glad!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.25,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard too!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.50,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw pictures to match \Nyour amazing stories!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.04,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which story do you wanna do then?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.69,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,"Two Earths," I think.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.08,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,"Sunglasses" is better for serialization.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.08,0:06:05.63,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.18,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have an ideal page count in mind?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.18,0:06:12.34,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the New Artist of the Year \Naward limits works to 31-45 pages.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.64,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds about right.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.86,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry about that right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.86,0:06:17.87,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Just write!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.56,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.71,0:06:29.28,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Finished already?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.38,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, 'cause I had the beginning \Nthought out already.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.27,0:06:37.08,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's not interesting, \Na fast pace does nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.13,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.13,0:06:44.81,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.33,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.94,0:06:50.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a sec!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.98,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're being paged.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.01,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I wanna go.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.53,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's coming over here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.18,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.31,Q_Q,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring people when they call you...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.13,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,She looks really pissed...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.61,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.49,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,What about?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.56,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, stay!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.24,0:07:16.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Miho asked me, "Why does Takagi \Nknow about my dream for the future?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You told him, didn't you?"
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She got angry at me, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.62,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't really matter, does it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.67,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was confirm it with her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.80,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I did tell him by accident though.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.35,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is my friend Mashiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.89,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.89,0:07:33.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Miho's easily embarrassed, so \NI told you not to tell anyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.83,0:07:41.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But you ask her, how's she gonna \Nbe a voice actor if she's that shy?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.13,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could say that.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.13,0:07:46.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I won't tell anyone \Nelse, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.87,0:07:49.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So, she turned you down?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But you talked to her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it was just to confirm \Nif that was really her dream or not.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Azuki already has \Nsomeone she likes, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Who?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! But it's normal for middle \Nschool girls to like someone, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.19,0:08:11.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But she never talks about it though.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you ask me about her then?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me think about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.29,0:08:30.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you've done it now.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.58,0:08:33.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that was a joke, there's \Ngonna be tears or pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.01,0:08:41.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's participated in national karate \Nor aikido tournaments, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.40,0:08:45.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And she's always liked you, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.77,0:08:50.43,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She told you her best friend's \Nsecret. Doesn't that mean something?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And her "Let me think about that."
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If she actually hated you, \Nshe'd never say that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is bad!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi's not bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad? Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's best friend can't be bad!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.00,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.64,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi confessed to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.64,0:09:12.49,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.24,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.82,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of him?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.23,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,He's smart and tall...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.22,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! We don't match at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.80,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! You're cute, Kaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.46,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Takagi thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.61,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... cute?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.21,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.66,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.50,0:09:40.98,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But according to the rumors, \Nhe's definitely with Iwase.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.21,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,But she's probably hard for guys to approach.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.46,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Her whole "boys are so beneath me" attitude?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.46,0:09:49.94,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's not that—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.40,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.12,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you like?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.12,0:09:54.81,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.90,Default,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No one.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.74,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I thought!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.68,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's looking at us!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.25,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and spill it!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.49,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,No one, I said!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.41,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Guys will think you're stuck up \Nlike Iwase if you keep saying that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.09,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.25,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever seen you talk to a boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.21,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that kind of snobby?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.41,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.01,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.51,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just too embarrassed to talk to guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.94,0:10:24.50,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I like guys \Neven more than you do!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.50,0:10:24.81,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.86,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I don't have \Nany brothers or something,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.86,0:10:31.77,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm really aware of guys, so I blush \Nreally easily and can't talk to them.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.69,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.22,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny when you talk \Nlike a teacher, Miho.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.11,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.27,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But because you spoke so earnestly, I get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.98,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not lying.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.03,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.33,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you go by yourself \Nto talk to Takagi!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.03,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.60,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go with you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.88,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.39,0:10:54.96,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,They're back!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.81,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.26,Default,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.26,Default,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.28,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're on the same wavelength too.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.85,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,That was just her turning around.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.45,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "just"?
