Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It never ends!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.46,0:11:27.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I rewrite \Nit, I'm still not satisfied.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And it's almost summer break already.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stress about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.65,0:11:34.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough to turn \Nit into a manuscript anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.61,0:11:39.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine if you finish the second \Nhalf when I'm done with the first half.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.56,0:11:41.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got it.
