Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:46.47,Ranking,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz17.334\frx20\fry348\move(223,24,223,230,0,4365)}Rankings
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.98,0:11:45.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sixth place! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.47,Ranking,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx0\fry358\frz18.325\move(213,-5,213,113)}1st Semester Final Exam
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just out of our class.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you said, there's \Na pattern to exam questions.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right, all that's left is...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Our wavelengths...
