Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.41,Vacation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,257)}I don't wanna do homework
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.41,Vacation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(532,121)\c&H54554B&}Class over summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.41,Vacation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H54554B&\pos(598,141)}Eww
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your father might have agreed,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.23,0:12:13.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but you should know {\i1}I'm{\i0} against you spending \Nall summer locked up in that studio.
