Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.58,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come home sometimes, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.20,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saiko!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay over, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.99,0:12:33.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but don't your parents care?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taro Kawaguchi drank this \Nto help him focus, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should try it too!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.69,0:12:45.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty into these rituals, huh.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, once again.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,To completing a manuscript \Nthis summer vacation!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.94,0:12:52.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers to that!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.92,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,That's bitter...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.52,0:13:01.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! My name's becoming a manga!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is still a name.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just fixing the layout \Nand composition a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.86,0:13:08.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like once you take a pen \Nto it, it'll become an amazing manga!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.68,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's still far from completion.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We still have the rough draft after this.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a while until I take a pen to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're not at that stage yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.10,0:13:21.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep practicing up until \Nthe second I do it in pen.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But Saiko, you said there aren't \Nany boundaries in manga.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.70,0:13:25.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're \Ntrying a little too hard?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're already—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not even close.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do it to your satisfaction.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I keep working on names \Ntill I'm satisfied too!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.58,0:13:38.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a word about the names.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And you won't say a word about the pictures.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.02,0:13:44.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You asleep, Saiko?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could fall asleep that quickly.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we used our brains \Nso much we {\i1}can't{\i0} sleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll read some more manga.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Going to read in your sleep?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Read anything interesting lately?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonball.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You already liked that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's loyalty. Or maybe 'cause \Nit's the crux of everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.90,0:14:26.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever pretend like you were \Nin Dragonball when you were little?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I did!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.21,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Fu...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.16,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,sion!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.16,0:14:31.94,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Ha!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.98,0:14:36.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shujin, you were late on the "sion"!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My "sion" was perfect!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your "sion" was too early!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.43,0:14:44.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No! If you don't say it with enough \Nenergy, it's not the real thing!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you calling my "sion" fake?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.18,0:14:49.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who's John anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.81,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
