Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shujin.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try using a pen.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a month.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.49,0:15:15.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not completely satisfied, \Nbut it's time to start.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying you need to hurry the names.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You should keep at it until you're satisfied.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I finished the first half.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. You should take a break!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.25,0:15:59.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if whiteout can fix this...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out for a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.73,0:16:34.05,News,Radio,0000,0000,0000,,And now, for this week's number one hit...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.05,0:16:38.52,News,Radio,0000,0000,0000,,Released in July, it's already \Nalmost platinum, Koji's...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you just love this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fscy150\fs20\pos(633,364)\c&HFFFFFF&}Limited {\c&H4E45BD&}Time Only 360 Yen
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's Koji, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's a song from his new album!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.32,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see his summer tour!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we've got to live \Nit up over summer break!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shujin?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get back to work.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to sleep soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.35,Q_Q,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's already done this much?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.05,0:17:59.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it took this long.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Take a break!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can get the groceries.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,After this, I won't be working on \Nthe manuscript anymore, so let me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.92,0:18:17.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you called Azuki, \NI'm sure she'd come over.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.30,0:18:22.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"Master, your meal is ready."
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding, I'm kidding!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that would perk you up a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.10,0:18:33.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I know Azuki's not that type of girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'd like to get this book...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You sure took a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't go to the nearby store?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's from the usual place.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You got Jack!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.18,0:19:06.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Eiji Nizuma!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Eiji's amazing.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just his drawings. \NHis story's good too.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If we were...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,to lose right now...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,it's 'cause of our drawings!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.83,0:19:33.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saiko!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna lose.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.01,0:19:39.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, but for illustrations to \Nbe as interesting as the story...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.93,0:19:40.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can help with?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You completed the names all by yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna complete this by myself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(\fscy95\fscx85)\bord0\fs15\b1\fnBPreplay\frx36\fry0\frz26.974\c&H536646&\move(280,58,303,90,0,1531)}Middle School\N{\fs30\c&HE0F0EB&}Math
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The whiteout's done.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko, I can hel—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.34,0:20:51.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a word about the names.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And you won't say a word \Nabout the pictures, remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.36,0:20:58.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was just hoping to work towards \Nthat moment of completion together...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Can you apply screentone?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.07,0:21:03.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Apply this to the pants \Nof every Earth soldier!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's full speed until we finish!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.76,0:21:13.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The drawings are good but I \Ndon't know about my story.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.99,0:21:35.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The story's good but I'm \Nnot sure about my drawings.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.24,0:21:42.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What're doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.11,0:21:57.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Saiko.
